The Escuela de los Commons (E2C) - or School of the Commons - is developing research and educational activities on the Commons and based on peer production and commons-based models.

Originally, work started in Spanish and Catalan, due to the origins of the initiative (Barcelona). But in order to work as a node in the global commons network, English is used for the core design parts.

